  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1204040/extras/1de85303a4702ff14b8621b51263781a.avif?t=1758073539\" width=600 height=85 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1204040/extras/57c4be26bf389410db07985d42f2efdb.poster.avif?t=1758073539\" width=580 height=326 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1204040/extras/57c4be26bf389410db07985d42f2efdb.webm?t=1758073539\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1204040/extras/57c4be26bf389410db07985d42f2efdb.mp4?t=1758073539\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Decades of rule by the rich have left the world on the brink of collapse. With oppression and corruption running rampant, the people have finally had enough. The Stagers lead the revolution to bring The System down and will stop at nothing to bring justice to this world, facing the most elite agents mustered by the wealthy to defend their ill-gotten gains. Who will you fight for?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Shoot on Sight is a near-future isometric tactical shooter for competitive PVP, cooperative PVE, and solo play, where good tactics matter far more than a big gun. Fight for the future of society on dynamic maps, outsmart your opponents, and remember: Shoot on sight!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1204040/extras/15fb74848a005c5b4de606f460e3751b.avif?t=1758073539\" width=600 height=85 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1204040/extras/fa8a1a1a773cbfd28f718d027edb4250.poster.avif?t=1758073539\" width=580 height=326 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1204040/extras/fa8a1a1a773cbfd28f718d027edb4250.webm?t=1758073539\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1204040/extras/fa8a1a1a773cbfd28f718d027edb4250.mp4?t=1758073539\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1204040/extras/3d5837da1cc902a512ebc7300c6b15d0.avif?t=1758073539\" width=600 height=85 /></span>The System controls the world, lording over unchecked corruption, extreme inequality, and brutal oppression. Against its elite agents stand the Stagers, rebels fighting for a just world for everyone.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1204040/extras/84093f7437cda1e5f72145188e883d7b.avif?t=1758073539\" width=600 height=85 /></span>Fight the rebels as an elite police agent - or stoke the fires of rebellion as one of twelve distinct characters with unique abilities, unlocks, and backstories to discover.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1204040/extras/da6f44785ed5ef3a9d2ff4fe06e52dc1.avif?t=1758073539\" width=600 height=85 /></span>Customize your loadout to fit your playstyle. Bring overwhelming firepower to suppress the enemy. Wade into their ranks with a sledgehammer. Nail them with a well-placed shot through the door just as they're about to breach. The only limit is your imagination.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1204040/extras/2064b51bc68da48174b2f4cbeccd2801.avif?t=1758073539\" width=600 height=85 /></span>Walls can be destroyed, windows and doors breached, and almost every object on the map used creatively to gain an edge over your opponent. Wounds leave blood trails, allowing you to stalk your foes - or draw the enemy into a trap, just as they think you are on your last legs.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1204040/extras/4be89db5dffb511e562cd8c8b1e0b9ef.avif?t=1758073539\" width=600 height=85 /></span>Whether you play on your own, face other players or fight alongside them in 4-player multiplayer modes, you're never alone. As the war for the future of society rages on, you'll be surrounded by computer-controlled friends and foes, keeping you on your toes.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1204040/extras/d6d2d801455ef31dee4ff6ec7317d0c4.avif?t=1758073539\" width=600 height=85 /></span>Whether you win or lose, every match brings you closer to unlocking new weapons, gadgets, attachments, character abilities, and reveals more about the epic conflict at the heart of Shoot on Sight.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1204040/extras/9085f502e32d068a51b7033bc853aeb1.poster.avif?t=1758073539\" width=580 height=326 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1204040/extras/9085f502e32d068a51b7033bc853aeb1.webm?t=1758073539\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1204040/extras/9085f502e32d068a51b7033bc853aeb1.mp4?t=1758073539\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1204040/extras/1de85303a4702ff14b8621b51263781a.avif?t=1758073539\" width=600 height=85 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1204040/extras/57c4be26bf389410db07985d42f2efdb.poster.avif?t=1758073539\" width=580 height=326 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1204040/extras/57c4be26bf389410db07985d42f2efdb.webm?t=1758073539\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1204040/extras/57c4be26bf389410db07985d42f2efdb.mp4?t=1758073539\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Decades of rule by the rich have left the world on the brink of collapse. With oppression and corruption running rampant, the people have finally had enough. The Stagers lead the revolution to bring The System down and will stop at nothing to bring justice to this world, facing the most elite agents mustered by the wealthy to defend their ill-gotten gains. Who will you fight for?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Shoot on Sight is a near-future isometric tactical shooter for competitive PVP, cooperative PVE, and solo play, where good tactics matter far more than a big gun. Fight for the future of society on dynamic maps, outsmart your opponents, and remember: Shoot on sight!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1204040/extras/15fb74848a005c5b4de606f460e3751b.avif?t=1758073539\" width=600 height=85 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1204040/extras/fa8a1a1a773cbfd28f718d027edb4250.poster.avif?t=1758073539\" width=580 height=326 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1204040/extras/fa8a1a1a773cbfd28f718d027edb4250.webm?t=1758073539\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1204040/extras/fa8a1a1a773cbfd28f718d027edb4250.mp4?t=1758073539\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1204040/extras/3d5837da1cc902a512ebc7300c6b15d0.avif?t=1758073539\" width=600 height=85 /></span>The System controls the world, lording over unchecked corruption, extreme inequality, and brutal oppression. Against its elite agents stand the Stagers, rebels fighting for a just world for everyone.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1204040/extras/84093f7437cda1e5f72145188e883d7b.avif?t=1758073539\" width=600 height=85 /></span>Fight the rebels as an elite police agent - or stoke the fires of rebellion as one of twelve distinct characters with unique abilities, unlocks, and backstories to discover.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1204040/extras/da6f44785ed5ef3a9d2ff4fe06e52dc1.avif?t=1758073539\" width=600 height=85 /></span>Customize your loadout to fit your playstyle. Bring overwhelming firepower to suppress the enemy. Wade into their ranks with a sledgehammer. Nail them with a well-placed shot through the door just as they're about to breach. The only limit is your imagination.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1204040/extras/2064b51bc68da48174b2f4cbeccd2801.avif?t=1758073539\" width=600 height=85 /></span>Walls can be destroyed, windows and doors breached, and almost every object on the map used creatively to gain an edge over your opponent. Wounds leave blood trails, allowing you to stalk your foes - or draw the enemy into a trap, just as they think you are on your last legs.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1204040/extras/4be89db5dffb511e562cd8c8b1e0b9ef.avif?t=1758073539\" width=600 height=85 /></span>Whether you play on your own, face other players or fight alongside them in 4-player multiplayer modes, you're never alone. As the war for the future of society rages on, you'll be surrounded by computer-controlled friends and foes, keeping you on your toes.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1204040/extras/d6d2d801455ef31dee4ff6ec7317d0c4.avif?t=1758073539\" width=600 height=85 /></span>Whether you win or lose, every match brings you closer to unlocking new weapons, gadgets, attachments, character abilities, and reveals more about the epic conflict at the heart of Shoot on Sight.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1204040/extras/9085f502e32d068a51b7033bc853aeb1.poster.avif?t=1758073539\" width=580 height=326 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1204040/extras/9085f502e32d068a51b7033bc853aeb1.webm?t=1758073539\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1204040/extras/9085f502e32d068a51b7033bc853aeb1.mp4?t=1758073539\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
